thread.title: Anna Gao
thread.title_full: Trade Tested reviewed by Anna Gao

author: Anna Gao
title: Anna Gao
text: I bought a 60cm*60am 6-panel dog exercise pen from trade tested through courier post. The material is tested to be very strong and reliable. A few days later, I bought another 8 panel dog exercise pen from another store on the way home. when the later pen was put together with the one bought earlier, the difference is very noticable - the material is softer and thinner.
